                <p>One of Kerala’s most iconic beaches, Kovalam is known for its crescent-shaped coastline, golden sands, and calm blue waters. The lighthouse, serene sunsets, and vibrant beachside cafés make it the perfect destination for relaxation and photography.</p>
                <p class="mb-30">Located just 15 km from Trivandrum, Kovalam offers opportunities for swimming, Ayurvedic massages, and seafood dining — a must-visit for every traveler seeking coastal bliss.</p>
