                <div class="section-title">Padmanabhaswamy <span>Temple</span></div>
                <p>Dedicated to Lord Vishnu, the Padmanabhaswamy Temple is one of the richest and most sacred temples in the world. Its magnificent Dravidian-style architecture and divine ambiance attract thousands of devotees and visitors every year.</p>
                <p class="mb-30">Situated in the heart of Trivandrum, this temple is a blend of devotion, history, and intricate craftsmanship — a must-visit for both spiritual seekers and culture enthusiasts.</p>
